### Third-Space API - Inbox/Notifications Endpoints
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = {{baseUrl}}
@apiKey = {{apiKey}}

### ============================================
### INBOX SUMMARY
### ============================================

### Get inbox summary (unread count, total count)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inbox/summary
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### ============================================
### LIST NOTIFICATIONS
### ============================================

### List all notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inbox/notifications
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### List notifications with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inbox/notifications?limit=20
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### List notifications with cursor
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inbox/notifications?cursor=2024-01-15T10:30:00Z&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### List only unread notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inbox/notifications?unread_only=true
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### ============================================
### MARK AS READ
### ============================================

### Mark a specific notification as read (replace NOTIFICATION_ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inbox/notifications/NOTIFICATION_ID_HERE/read
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Mark all notifications as read
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inbox/notifications/mark-all-read
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### ============================================
### DELETE NOTIFICATION
### ============================================

### Delete a specific notification (replace NOTIFICATION_ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inbox/notifications/NOTIFICATION_ID_HERE
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
